snippet.title: Myst 25th Anniversary Collection
snippet.description: It's been 25 years since Myst first arrived. To celebrate, Cyan announces a limited-time, limited-run, uniquely packaged collection of all of the Myst games, with some amazing artifacts - only through Kickstarter.  #myst25 http://kck.st/2EwUP33
